parcel.name: ApeCoin Unofficial Dao parcel
parcel.description:
"Going down the Apehole" Metaverse parcel in Voxels.com

This is a parcel to experience, to educate, entertain and bring together the community.

It will serve the purpose of Educating people about Apecoin and also have space to show a virtual gallery, inspired by ApeCoin. Voxels has an eclectic mix of early adopters in the culture of web3 who will learn and engage about APE and the ApeCoin Dao.

features.text:
#How can I submit an AIP?
You can submit an AIP by visiting the ApeCoin DAO forum on Discourse (not to be confused with Discord or Snapshot). Comprehensive guidelines on drafting and submitting AIPs are available on the website and forum under the "Start Here" section.

#Which ApeCoin DAO Community Initiatives can I participate in, today?
Currently, you can get involved in the following community initiatives:

#What are Working Groups?
Working Groups are structured community-led initiatives designed to facilitate the execution of mandates approved by the DAO. Each Working Group is guided by a Charter that outlines its specific mandate, which must align with the vision and values of the ApeCoin DAO.
